%H A397818 Charles H. C. Little, Kee L. Teo, and Bruce Van Brunt, <a href="https://doi.org/10.1007/978-3-030-90646-7">An introduction to infinite products</a>, New York: Springer, 2022. See p. 234.
%H A397818 Thomas J. Osler, <a href="https://www.fq.math.ca/Papers1/45-3/osler.pdf">Vieta-like products of nested radicals with Fibonacci and Lucas numbers</a>, The Fibonacci Quarterly, Vol. 45, No. 3 (2007), pp. 202-204.
