%H A397818 <a href="/index/Tra#transcendental">Index entries for transcendental numbers</a>.
%F A397818 Equals (n/F(n)) * sqrt(1/2 + L(n)/4) * sqrt(1/2 + sqrt(1/2 + L(n)/4)/2) * sqrt(1/2 + sqrt(1/2 + sqrt(1/2 + L(n)/4)/2)/2) * ... for n even >= 2, where F(n) = A000045(n) and L(n) = A000032(n) (Osler, 2007).
%F A397818 Equals (phi - 1/2)/log(phi).
%F A397818 Equals A002163/(2*A002390) = A002163/A202543 = A002163*A160509/2.
%F A397818 Equals A002163 * A397819.
%e A397818 2.323371809517386399509704839729899944452231719648431...
%t A397818 RealDigits[Sqrt[5]/2/Log[GoldenRatio], 10, 120][[1]]
%o A397818 (PARI) my(phi = quadgen(5)); sqrt(5)/(2*log(phi))
